{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"body":"Twelfth remediation: placed prerequisite_attribution_valid unambiguously inside verification.binary with exact helper signatures and key path; named the existing finders batch as the sole coverage producer; defined PrerequisiteVerificationBlock and its packing formula; specified coachable filtering and all four YAML call sites; added the existing container eval and offline test as concrete compatibility oracles."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1784571833921734001,"uuid":"85903d73-e5ad-4b76-bb06-f91821ad18fd"}